      "releaseNotes": {
        "releaseNotesTooltip": "<div><span class=\"tooltip-title\">What's new in RAPIDS 25.12 - Stable:</span><ul><li>Support for PyArrow backed dtypes in Pandas, bringing acceleration to \"Arrow-based\" pandas workflows</li><li>Polars Single GPU Polars has experimental streaming and adds window functions and file writer support, a key feature for data engineering workloads (data science workloads less likely to need file writers)</li><li>RAPIDS singleCell 0.13.5 adds support for multi-GPU clustering via Dask to tl.leiden and tl.louvain </li></ul><a href=\"https://rapids.ai/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"tooltip-link\">Open Release Notes</a></div>",
